_sText:
This is my first map to use custom textures. They were all created by me and are included in the map files themselves. I'm not sure if people will like the textures at all, but I don't feel like re-texturing this map so I'm just releasing it as is. It's mostly very close quarters so this map if a good rushing map. If you like it or hate it, please leave a comment anyway! :)

Btw, I don't know how to make a custom skybox so I just used a stock one. I hope it doesn't take away from the look too much.

**buyzones included for use without gg mod.
